# worldspec — permanent identifiers for the WorldSpec specification
#
# WorldSpec is a declarative language for modeling software systems as
# entities, relationships, states, invariants, actions, and transitions.
# Its specification, namespace document, and JSON Schemas are published via
# GitHub Pages. These redirects provide stable w3id.org identifiers that can be
# repointed (R=302) if the hosting location later changes.
#
# Project: https://github.com/banuap/worldspec
# Site:    https://banuap.github.io/worldspec/
#
# ## Contact
# Banu Parasuraman
# banu.parasuraman@mphasis.com
# GitHub username: banuap

RewriteEngine on
RewriteRule ^(.*)$ https://banuap.github.io/worldspec/$1 [R=302,L,NE]
